	<key>NSAudioCaptureUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Volume Mixer routes each app's audio through itself to give you an independent volume slider per application.</string>
	<key>NSMicrophoneUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Volume Mixer needs audio-capture access to control the volume of individual applications.</string>
</dict>
